stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_gas: available_gas >= 6900
    q_check_gas --> q_charge: available_gas >= 6900
    q_check_gas --> q_oog: available_gas < 6900
    q_oog --> [*]: revert out-of-gas
    q_charge --> q_execute: remaining_gas = available_gas - 6900
    q_execute --> q_return_success: execution returns result
    q_execute --> q_return_fail: execution returns empty
    q_return_success --> [*]: return result (gas consumed = 6900)
    q_return_fail --> [*]: return empty (gas consumed = 6900)
